\begin_layout Remark
对于拓展的四维泡利矩阵矢量
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma,\bar{\sigma}$
\end_inset

满足关系
\begin_inset Formula $\left(p\cdot\sigma\right)\left(p\cdot\bar{\sigma}\right)=p^{2}$
\end_inset

，类似地，对于
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma$
\end_inset

矩阵，
\begin_inset Formula $\left(p\cdot\gamma\right)\left(p\cdot\gamma\right)=p^{2}$
\end_inset

