\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
zee：
\series default
对于狄拉克方程
\begin_inset Formula $\left(i\gamma\cdot\partial-m\right)\psi\left(x\right)=0$
\end_inset

左边乘上
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{0}$
