\begin_layout Standard
在理论物理中，拉里塔-施温格方程 是相对论性的，自旋
\begin_inset Formula $3/2$
\end_inset

费米子的场方程。它和自旋
\begin_inset Formula $1/2$
\end_inset

粒子的狄拉克方程类似。该方程于 1941 年由 William Rarita 和 Julian Schwinger 引入，用现在的记号表示是：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\alpha}\gamma^{5}\gamma_{\nu}\partial_{\rho}\psi_{\alpha}+m\psi^{\mu}=0\\
\Rightarrow & -\varepsilon^{\mu\rho\alpha\nu}\gamma_{\nu}\gamma^{5}\partial_{\rho}\psi_{\alpha}+m\psi^{\mu}=0\\
\text{指标重写}\quad\Rightarrow & -\varepsilon^{\mu\rho\nu\alpha}\gamma_{\alpha}\gamma^{5}\partial_{\rho}\psi_{\nu}+m\psi^{\mu}=0\\
\Rightarrow & \varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\alpha}\gamma_{\alpha}\gamma^{5}\partial_{\rho}\psi_{\nu}+m\psi^{\mu}=0
\end{align*}

\end_inset

以上，
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}$
\end_inset

是 Levi-Civita 符号，
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{\nu}$
\end_inset

是狄拉克矩阵，
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

是质量，
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{\mu}$
\end_inset

 是旋量组成的矢量（vector–valued spinor）。相比于普通的狄拉克四分量旋量，
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{\mu}$
\end_inset

 具有额外分量。它是洛伦兹群表示按如下方式直乘与直和的结果：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\frac{1}{2},\frac{1}{2}\right)\otimes\left(\left(\frac{1}{2},0\right)\oplus\left(0,\frac{1}{2}\right)\right)
\]

\end_inset

或者说，它的
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(1,\frac{1}{2}\right)\oplus\left(\frac{1}{2},1\right)
\]

\end_inset

部分。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
使用 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \gamma^{\rho},\sigma^{\mu\nu}\right\} =-2\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\alpha}\gamma_{\alpha}\gamma^{5}$
\end_inset

 得：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
-\frac{1}{2}\left\{ \gamma^{\rho},\sigma^{\mu\nu}\right\} \partial_{\rho}\psi_{\nu}+m\psi^{\mu}=0
\]

\end_inset

若认为
\begin_inset Formula $\psi^{\mu}$
\end_inset

满足
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{\mu}\psi_{\mu}=0$
\end_inset

，则有：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sigma^{\mu\nu}\psi_{\nu}=\frac{i}{2}\left(\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}-\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\mu}\right)\psi_{\nu}=\frac{i}{2}\left(-2g^{\mu\nu}\right)\psi_{\nu}=-i\psi^{\mu}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & -\frac{1}{2}\left\{ \gamma^{\rho},\sigma^{\mu\nu}\right\} \partial_{\rho}\psi_{\nu}+im\sigma^{\mu\nu}\psi_{\nu}=0\\
\Rightarrow & \frac{-i}{2}\left\{ \gamma^{\rho},\sigma^{\mu\nu}\right\} \partial_{\rho}\psi_{\nu}-m\left(-i\sigma^{\mu\nu}\right)\psi_{\nu}=0
\end{align*}

\end_inset

若令
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\gamma^{\mu\nu}=\frac{1}{2}\left[\gamma^{\mu},\gamma^{\nu}\right]=-i\sigma^{\mu\nu},\qquad\gamma^{\mu\nu\rho}=\frac{1}{2}\left\{ \gamma^{\mu\nu},\gamma^{\rho}\right\} =-\frac{i}{2}\left\{ \sigma^{\mu\nu},\gamma^{\rho}\right\} 
\]

\end_inset

则回到我们使用的形式：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(i\gamma^{\mu\nu\rho}\partial_{\rho}-m\gamma^{\mu\nu}\right)T_{\nu}=0
\]

\end_inset

上面的场方程可以从如下拉氏量导出：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathcal{L}=\frac{1}{2}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\alpha}\overline{\psi}_{\mu}\gamma^{5}\gamma_{\nu}\partial_{\rho}\psi_{\alpha}-m\overline{\psi}_{\mu}\psi^{\mu}=\overline{\psi}_{\mu}\left(\frac{1}{2}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\alpha}\gamma^{5}\gamma_{\nu}\partial_{\rho}g_{\alpha}^{\beta}-mg^{\mu\beta}\right)\psi_{\beta}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{\psi}$
\end_inset

是狄拉克伴随表示（adjoint）。如同狄拉克方程的情形，可以通过将普通导数升至协变导数，引入电磁相互作用
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\partial_{\mu}\to D_{\mu}=\partial_{\mu}-ieQA_{\mu}
\]

\end_inset

无质量的 Rarita–Schwinger 方程具有规范对称性，在定域规范变换
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{\mu}\to\psi_{\mu}+\partial_{\mu}\varepsilon$
\end_inset

下不变，其中
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon$
\end_inset

是任意旋量场。
\end_layout

