\end_inset

 是一组依赖于动量 
\begin_inset Formula $p^{\mu}$
\end_inset

 的极化矢量，它在任意坐标系中满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p_{\mu}\epsilon_{\mu}^{i}\left(p\right)=0.\quad\Rightarrow\partial_{\mu}A^{\mu}=0.
\]

\end_inset

对于任意满足
\begin_inset Formula $p^{2}=m^{2}$
\end_inset

的四矢量
\begin_inset Formula $p^{\mu}$
\end_inset

，上面的方程有三个线性独立的 
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon_{\mu}^{i}\left(p\right)$
\end_inset

。通常将极化矢量归一化到
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon_{\mu}^{*}\epsilon^{\mu}=-1$
\end_inset

。例如选取 
\begin_inset Formula $p^{\mu}$
\end_inset

 沿着
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

轴，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p^{\mu}=\left(E,0,0,p_{z}\right),\quad E^{2}-p_{z}^{2}=m^{2},
\]

\end_inset

则两个容易看出来的，满足 
\begin_inset Formula $p_{\mu}\epsilon_{\mu}=0$
\end_inset

 且 
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon^{\mu}\epsilon_{\mu}=-1$
\end_inset

的解是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\epsilon^{\mu,1}=\left(0,1,0,0\right),\quad\epsilon^{\mu,2}=\left(0,0,1,0\right).
\]

\end_inset

它们就是横向极化。另一个解是纵向极化：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\epsilon_{\mu}^{L}=\left(\frac{p_{z}}{m},0,0,\frac{E}{m}\right).
\]

\end_inset

这三个极化矢量 
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon_{\mu}^{i}\left(p\right)$
\end_inset

 ，构成了洛伦兹群的不可约表示。此basis 依赖于 
\begin_inset Formula $p^{\mu}$
\end_inset

，由于动量的连续变化的，所以是无穷维表示。将这些基向量对于 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
